-- Chile’s CSAV Arranges $90 Million 12-Year Loan From DVB Bank
-- B y   S e b a s t i a n   B o y d
-- 2012-06-13T16:14:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-13/chile-s-csav-arranges-90-million-12-year-loan-from-dvb-bank.html
Cia. Sud Americana de Vapores SA,
 Chile ’s biggest container shipping company, arranged a $90
million 12-year loan from  DVB Bank SE (DVB) , a Frankfurt-based lender
specializing in transport finance.  The company will use the funds to purchase the last two
ships of seven container vessels it ordered from Samsung Heavy
Industries Co., Vapores said today in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sebastian Boyd in Santiago at 
 sboyd9@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
